name: r-lemon
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.4.5" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-lemon
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/lemon_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/lemon/lemon_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: c4d3d0dedf9d0147aa63813ec3277a40a0af0017f25aa13ced53350c5b9474f8

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-ggplot2 >=3.3.0
    - r-gridextra
    - r-gtable
    - r-knitr >=1.12
    - r-lattice
    - r-plyr
    - r-rlang
    - r-scales
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-ggplot2 >=3.3.0
    - r-gridextra
    - r-gtable
    - r-knitr >=1.12
    - r-lattice
    - r-plyr
    - r-rlang
    - r-scales

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('lemon')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('lemon')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/stefanedwards/lemon
  license: GPL-3.0-only
  summary: Functions for working with legends and axis lines of 'ggplot2', facets that repeat axis lines on all panels, and some 'knitr' extensions.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
